    "Thanks for making such a great breakfast every morning.\""
    
    "I bring my hands together in thanks."
    
    "\"Preparing meals is Nee-san's duty."
    
    "If you wish to compliment the meal, please tell Nee-san instead.\""
    
    "\"That's true, but---your duties are really completely separate?"
    
    "Such as like today when only I slept in, I thought you might make it.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T08.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"Shiki-sama, are you saying the breakfast was not to your taste?\""
    
    "\"----Eh?\""
    
    "Her words are so off topic it's.. troubling."
    
    "Does she think I was saying I wanted her to make breakfast because the breakfast tasted so bad?"
    
    "\"That's not it."
    
    "Even cold, Kohaku-san's cooking is delicious."
    
    ".... But, I like it when it's warm."
    
    "And, it'd make me really happy if I got to taste your cooking, Hisui.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"---I cannot do that."
    
    "Shiki-sama, I refuse to cook for you.\""
    
    "Hey eyes suddenly take on a challenging look."
    
    "\"Oh, I, see."
    
    "Yeah, I don't want to force you to do anything you don't want to do."
    
    "You already do so much for me already.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T05.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"........\""
    
    "Still silent, she faces me as if she wants to say something."
    
    ".... What could it be?"
    
    "Is it something that's difficult for her to say?"
    
    "\"What's wrong Hisui?"
    
    "Did I do something bad without realizing it again?\""
    
    "Hisui shakes her head \"no\"."
    
    "She just stands there silently."
    
    "\".... Then, I'll go back to my room."
    
    "If you need me, please call for me.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\"Later,\" I say as I start to walk out of the room."
    
    "But---before that, Hisui walks towards the lobby."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T01.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"---Shiki-sama.\""
    
    "\"Hm?\""
    
    "\"This may be impolite, but I wanted to fulfill your request to the best of my ability.\""
    
    "\".... Huh?\""
    
    "She looks directly at me."
    
    "\"This morning, I came to realize how powerless I am.\""
    
    "\"Eh---Uh?\""
    
    "\"Seven times."
    
    "I called out seven times, but there was no response."
    
    "Is this acceptable?\""
    
    "\"Seven times?"
    
    "What, do you mean?\""
    
    "I'm totally lost as to what she wants to say."
    
    "She turns around."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/HIS_T09.png' as i0 at fgpos(62, 0)
    
    "\"To say it candidly, I think you are very dense, Shiki-sama.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_34A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Hisui disappears into the lobby with her footsteps trailing in the air."
    
    "\"........ Huh?\""
    
    "Left by myself, I blurt out stupidly."
    
    "After thinking to myself for a while, I finally realize she was complaining to me."
    
    "---It's okay if you want to voice your complaints."
    
    "I said that earlier."
    
    "\"---That was.. my request?\""
    
    "Yeah, there's no mistake."
    
    "Hisui was thinking about it the whole time, and was waiting for me in the sitting room just to tell me."
    
    "\".......... Well, that is a complaint, but..\""
    
    "She said it, but saying \"dense\" is a little too blunt, right?"
    
    ".... I don't really want to think it,"
    
    "but does Hisui really hate me?"
    
