    "\"Akiha-sama, are you not going to call for a doctor?\""
    
    "\"Don't be stupid, Hisui."
    
    "There's no way I could do that, since Nii-san's wound isn't normal..!\""
    
    ".... Akiha  and  Hisui   are talking."
    
