    "\"Yes, you were unconscious since noon.\""
    
    "She speaks hesitantly."
    
    "I wasn't worried about me, but my promise to meet with Arcueid in the park at ten o'clock."
    
    "\"Oh no, I have to go."
    
    "Akiha, I have to go so I'll leave the rest to you."
    
    "Don't bully Hisui, okay?\""
    
    "\"D, don't say such stupid things....!"
    
    "I won't ask where you go every night, Nii-san."
    
    "I won't ask, so please at least tonight, take it easy on your body tonight....!\""
    
    "\"Haha, I'm okay."
    
    "This is pretty regular."
    
    "When I was in middle school, I used to collapse twice a day, you know that, right Akiha?\""
    
